###  http://www.di.uminho.pt/rpcw2026/PG61516#playingTimeMinutes
rpcw:playingTimeMinutes rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .


###  http://www.di.uminho.pt/rpcw2026/PG61516#year
rpcw:year rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .


